title: Hall of Fame Debate: Which current players will end up in Canton? (Football 12/26)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and Sean Wagner-McGough debate which current NFL players are destined for the Pro Football Hall of Fame. The discussion is centered around Eli Manning's future candidacy, as he returned to action for the Giants a few weeks ago. The guys also break down dozens of more players who could eventually end up in Canton.

*Note this episode was recorded prior to Week 15*
